reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I'm a journal snob - this checks every box
reviews.reviewText: I'm a total journal snob - I searched for this journal for no kidding probably 10 hours. (Yes, I know that's a poor use of my time, but here we are.) I'm not joking - this checks every box for what I was looking for: something sturdy, something large, something with dividers, something aesthetically pleasing.I use one notebook for all of my classes each semester at college, and carry this thing everywhere. Needless to say, it gets a lot of use and abuse. This thing held up incredibly well. The perforated pages are useful, but strong enough that they won't fall off when you're just using the pages. Thick paper that doesn't show through, even when using gel or thick pens. The dividers are useful but don't warp or break down over time like other journals I've used.Great purchase - I'll be getting another one again this year.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is the perfect notebook
reviews.reviewText: I love this notebook. I like having fancy notebooks for harder classes so I’m more motivated to use them. The quality is amazing and the color is gorgeous. The paper is pretty thick and doesn’t tear easily.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Love this notebook, it’s sturdy, large, and a great price! I purchased this book in black, my only complaint is that I wish they made this book in more neutral colors, I want to get more but as an adult I don’t want a pink or baby blue colored notebook. If they made this in brown, gray, a forest or moss green, navy blue I’d buy a bunch!

reviews.reviewText: Love the notebook, the color is perfect. It’s heavy & durable. Only thing I’d like to point out is although it says it’s a 3 subject notebook, it has 3 dividers but separates it into 4 sections instead of 3.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for bible journaling and this notebook is so cute! I love pink so this is perfect and it's like your average 5 star school notebook, with 8.5x11 sized and lined pages, just no hole punched holes. It does have a yellow tint though, for the pages just in case you're not a fan of yellow rather than white pages. I definitely will be getting more for future school years.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and Beautifully Holds All My Notes
reviews.reviewText: This notebook has thick pages that are easy to flip and don't bleed through. Nice, sturdy cover that I can hold in my hand and write notes instead of it flopping around like regular spiral notebooks. And I like that it has sections.I need this in more colors!!

One of the best notebooks I have had. I only have to suggest to add removable separators and a pocket.The sheets are perfect using markers and highlighters. Also is not as heavy as I thought which is good for my shoulders.
